    <item>
      <title>埃及货币大幅贬值的押注因国际货币基金组织加大一揽子计划的希望而破灭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/bets-on-big-fx-devaluation-in-egypt-crushed-as-government-nears-imf-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于埃及政府即将与国际货币基金组织(IMF)达成协议以扩大救助计划的规模，交易员们纷纷在今年年初解除对埃及货币大幅贬值的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/bets-on-big-fx-devaluation-in-egypt-crushed-as-government-nears-imf-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 08:45:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
