      <title>在前任丑闻发生后，英国石油公司任命奥金克洛斯为新任首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/bp-confirms-auchincloss-as-new-ceo-after-predecessor-s-scandal</link>
